      <title>耶伦警告美联储侵蚀美国民主威胁经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/yellen-warn-that-eroding-us-democracy-fed-threatens-economic-growth-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据财政部发布的讲话摘录，美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦将于周五发表讲话，称强大的民主机构——包括独立的美联储——是持续和共同增长与繁荣的关键基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/yellen-warn-that-eroding-us-democracy-fed-threatens-economic-growth-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 14:13:17 GMT</pubDate>
